t segment provides a suite of wealth, investment, trust, banking, credit, and other solutions to clients; asset management products to institutional and individual clients; and asset and investor services to financial institutions, asset managers, and asset owners. The company's Insurance segment offers life, health, travel, wealth, annuities, property and casualty, and reinsurance advice and solutions; digital platforms; and independent brokers and partners, as well as client-led advice and solutions. The company's Capital Markets segment offers advisory and origination, sales and trading, lending and financing, and transaction banking services to corporations, institutional clients, asset managers, private equity firms, and governments. The company was founded in 1864 and is based in Toronto, Canada.", "financialCurrency": "CAD", "totalRevenue": 63424000000, "grossProfits": 63424000000, "operatingIncome": null, "netIncomeToCommon": 20500000768, "country": "Canada"}, "currency": "CAD", "usd_rate": 0.7301934957504272}}